{"id":247141,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/08/维权网-鲁俊：还公民信访和举报的权利（图）/","date":"2012-08-15T10:30:44Z","modified":"2012-08-15T10:30:44Z","title":"维权网 | 鲁俊：还公民信访和举报的权利（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>根据《信访条例》规定，集体信访、走访的可推荐</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>名代表，享受接待。而上海市嘉定区安亭镇派出所警察用“告知书”的形式，威胁打击集体去北京的信访人员，歪曲事实，把集体举报控告行为说成是：“以抱团方式聚集上访。”</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">    </span></div>\n<div><span>警号为</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">047594</span><span>的安亭镇派出所警察对鲁俊的告知是在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2012</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">23</span><span>日</span><span>上午</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>时</span><span>。虽然“告知书”上没有公章，没有单位，没有任何笔迹，但是，鲁俊记下的警号不会错。该告知书中称，据公安机关掌握，你曾多次与他人一起进京聚集上访，希望你能听众规劝，对自己的行为负责，不要执迷不悟，一意孤行。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">    </span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">25</span><span>日</span><span>下午，在上海新客站，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">26</span><span>名嘉定区安亭镇村民，购买去北京的全程火车票，进行集体举报，结果进站后被嘉定区安亭镇信访办工作人员和安亭镇双浦村的干部堵截，不让村民去北京举报控告，当晚把村民带到安亭镇派出所限制人身自由。警察张宪峰（警号</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">047379</span><span>），对待举报人员张蕊蕊进行搜查，在其包中搜去</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">23</span><span>封实名举报信，时至</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>日</span><span>下午</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>时都没有把举报信件归还，在安亭镇派出所从下午关到次日凌晨</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>时不给吃饭，而且还把访民的身份证扣押</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">60</span><span>小时左右（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>天多），最后告知是：被双浦村副支书陆文斌扣押的。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">    </span></div>\n<div><span>综合上述事件，安亭镇派出所警察、安亭镇信访办工作人员和安亭镇双浦村委干部违反宪法赋予公民的信访权和举报权，如此堵截举报控告人员，对依法行使公民权利的上访群体进行威胁、关押，其目的只有一个，包庇和袒护安亭镇政府的贪污腐败行为。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>　　</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>希望有关部门依法查处违法国家宪法的侵权行为，还公民依法享有的信访权、举报权和人身自由权。</span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>整理人：鲁俊　　</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">2012</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13</span><span>日</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-a8sTRY_0jgk/UCtxlj_q-oI/AAAAAAAALX0/nTNt_YwmlrA/s1600/%25E6%25B0%2591%25E4%25BC%2597%25E8%25A6%2581%25E6%25B1%2582%25E4%25B8%25A5%25E6%2583%25A9%25E8%2585%2590%25E8%25B4%25A5%25E5%2588%2586%25E5%25AD%2590.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"195\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-a8sTRY_0jgk/UCtxlj_q-oI/AAAAAAAALX0/nTNt_YwmlrA/s320/%25E6%25B0%2591%25E4%25BC%2597%25E8%25A6%2581%25E6%25B1%2582%25E4%25B8%25A5%25E6%2583%25A9%25E8%2585%2590%25E8%25B4%25A5%25E5%2588%2586%25E5%25AD%2590.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>民众要求严惩腐败分子</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p></p>\n<table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-N2OQOjmMGmw/UCtxqIHZY9I/AAAAAAAALX8/D4JCp4E8skw/s1600/%25E9%25B2%2581%25E4%25BF%258A%25E6%2594%25B6%25E5%2588%25B0%25E7%259A%2584%25E7%259A%2584%25E5%2591%258A%25E7%259F%25A5%25E4%25B9%25A6.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-N2OQOjmMGmw/UCtxqIHZY9I/AAAAAAAALX8/D4JCp4E8skw/s320/%25E9%25B2%2581%25E4%25BF%258A%25E6%2594%25B6%25E5%2588%25B0%25E7%259A%2584%25E7%259A%2584%25E5%2591%258A%25E7%259F%25A5%25E4%25B9%25A6.jpg\" width=\"219\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>鲁俊收到的的告知书</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/751033951089627103-5530754131608196469?l=wqw2010.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=b4fd4ae247\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/mstlf\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18269,17850,20534],"tags":[16910,28519]}